reviewText: Works great and shipped super fast. It was great to relive my childhood for an hour and share this with my kids! :)
I had this when I was little and I was super excited to get it, but it was the wrong volume in the box. I still like the songs, but I wanted Hall & Oats. :(
its my favorite had it as a child and lost it when moving. glad i bought it you will enjoy it! i watch it often and sing along.
